WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.685
Hello, young word explorer.

2
00:00:01.685 --> 00:00:04.633
Welcome to Unit 8, Home, Sweet Home.

3
00:00:04.633 --> 00:00:08.844
This unit has 28 vocabulary cards in 5 learning groups.

4
00:00:08.844 --> 00:00:11.371
Group 1 is Types of Homes.

5
00:00:11.371 --> 00:00:16.424
Listen for words such as house, apartment, hut, tree house, nest, hive.

6
00:00:16.424 --> 00:00:19.372
Group 2 is Rooms in a Home.

7
00:00:19.372 --> 00:00:24.426
Listen for words such as bedroom, kitchen, bathroom, living room, dining room.

8
00:00:24.426 --> 00:00:26.953
Group 3 is Things at Home.

9
00:00:26.953 --> 00:00:31.585
Listen for words such as bed, table, chair, sofa, sink, rug.

10
00:00:31.585 --> 00:00:35.376
Group 4 is Jobs I Do at Home (Verbs).

11
00:00:35.376 --> 00:00:43.798
Listen for words such as make my bed, tidy my room, sweep the floor, set the table, wash the dishes.

12
00:00:43.798 --> 00:00:46.746
Group 5 is Homes Around the World.

13
00:00:46.746 --> 00:00:51.800
Listen for words such as adobe house, stilt house, cave house, skyscraper.

14
00:00:51.800 --> 00:01:02.329
For each word, listen and repeat, read five sentences, notice the word type, practise spelling, write your own sentence, and ask the tutor for help.

15
00:01:02.329 --> 00:01:05.277
You are ready to begin Unit 8.
